00:25:28.600 --> 00:25:30.840
[players shouting]

485
00:25:31.840 --> 00:25:34.720
[whistle blows]

486
00:25:34.800 --> 00:25:38.960
[Shaunagh] Getting it more accessible.
but also improving the product

487
00:25:39.040 --> 00:25:42.120
for people to want to watch it
rather than having to go looking for it.

488
00:25:54.320 --> 00:25:56.120
We're doing as much
as we can in the sport.

489
00:25:56.200 --> 00:25:57.160
There's always more to do.

490
00:25:57.240 --> 00:25:58.920
And I would like to think I do my bit.

491
00:25:59.000 --> 00:26:00.720
like having other people do
their bit as well.

492
00:26:00.800 --> 00:26:02.880
As long as we all do our bit
to promote the sport.

493
00:26:02.960 --> 00:26:05.120
[Victoria] There are so many things
in the game. that need to change

494
00:26:05.200 --> 00:26:08.360
but the one thing I think we all agree on
is that we need a kit for women.

495
00:26:08.440 --> 00:26:10.000
so why are still playing in men's kit?

496
00:26:10.080 --> 00:26:12.280
It doesn't fit and it doesn't work for us.

497
00:26:12.360 --> 00:26:14.640
[Stef] The reason that
it's so. in my opinion.

498
00:26:14.720 --> 00:26:17.800
inappropriate for women to wear
men's shorts to play and train in

