672
00:34:59.720 --> 00:35:02.680
whether it's rugby. tennis. football.
whatever it is.

673
00:35:02.760 --> 00:35:04.320
I just hope they have
a positive experience.

674
00:35:07.520 --> 00:35:10.960
We have the great game. but if there's
anything I can do to help better it.

675
00:35:11.040 --> 00:35:12.480
to help promote it.

676
00:35:12.560 --> 00:35:15.040
to help get more visibility. more eyes.

677
00:35:15.120 --> 00:35:18.080
inspire people to get involved in it
in any way. then.

678
00:35:18.160 --> 00:35:19.880
yeah. I definitely want to be that guy.

679
00:35:23.960 --> 00:35:27.120
It's easy to assume
that only girls follow us.

680
00:35:27.200 --> 00:35:30.840
But actually boys and men follow us. too.

681
00:35:30.920 --> 00:35:33.520
And it's becoming a bit more socially
acceptable for men

682
00:35:33.600 --> 00:35:36.400
to come up to us and say.
"Congratulations."

683
00:35:36.480 --> 00:35:39.240
I think sometimes. they might feel
