684
00:35:39.320 --> 00:35:41.360
like. following women's sport as a man

685
00:35:41.440 --> 00:35:43.520
but it's becoming
a lot more normal. thankfully.

686
00:35:45.720 --> 00:35:47.520
[Stef]
The most important thing I would like

